    Format[edit]

    • Group Stage: 4 groups of four teams in a double-elimination format.
      • Top 2 teams advance to Playoffs.
      • All matches are Bo3
    • Playoffs: 8 teams in a double-elimination bracket
      • All matches (excl. Grand Final and Lower Bracket Final) are Bo3
      • Lower Bracket Final and Grand Final are Bo5
